(77, 1, '2020-01-31 18:11:14', '2020-01-31 10:11:14', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>the coronavirus scare  <br>2020-01-22 ~ ...</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>the sars coronavirus!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Keep up the good work and hope you all take care of yourself during the coronavirus scare!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Epidemic prevention materials：<br>face mask<br>rubbing alcohol<br>hand sanitizer<br>paper towel<br>lysol spray<br>latex gloves<br>soft soap<br>clorox bleach<br>disinfectant wipes<br>diapers</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>outbreak 疫情爆发<br>under quarantine  隔离<br>surgical mask 医用口罩<br>N95 respiratory mask  N95口罩<br>symptom 症状<br>fever 发热<br>cough 咳嗽<br>Novel Coronavirus Pneumonia 新冠肺炎 (NCP)<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2020-03 update:<br>新型冠状病毒肺炎 COVID-19(Corona Virus Disease 2019)，简称“新冠肺炎”，世界卫生组织命名为“2019冠状病毒病”，是指2019新型冠状病毒感染导致的肺炎。2020年2月11日，世界卫生组织总干事谭德塞在瑞士日内瓦宣布，将新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎命名为“COVID-19”。<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'The coronavirus scare!', 'Keep up the good work and hope you all take care of yourself during the coronavirus scare!', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-coronavirus-scare', '', '', '2020-05-28 14:51:36', '2020-05-28 06:51:36', '', 0, 'http://www.hahafamily.com/?p=77', 0, 'post', '', 0),
